data.name: rdoBeginsWith.SuperTooltip
data.value: Select this option to search the database for items that begins with the entered character(s). For eg. entering 'ba' in the 'Name' field will find out all names starting with 'ba' like 'baiju', 'babu' etc.

data.name: chkShowPopups.SuperTooltip
data.value: Select this option to see Popup Messages near the system tray ( bottom right of the desktop) that gives you some information about the action performed. It is recommended that you keep this option selected.
